Class AD3Reasoner

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.umd.cs.psl.reasoner.ExecutableReasoner
      • edu.umd.cs.psl.reasoner.bool.AD3Reasoner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GroundKernelStore, Reasoner

    public class AD3Reasoner
extends ExecutableReasoner
    Reasoner that performs inferences as a Boolean MRF using the AD3 command-line executable (https://github.com/andre-martins/AD3). WARNING: This class is incomplete and not functional.
